SETUP INSTRUCTIONS FOR LIVE DM INGESTION
----------------------------------------------------------------------
To enable live DM monitoring, use ONE of these methods:

1. EMAIL FORWARDING (Recommended)
   - Forward YouTube DMs to a monitored email
   - Use an email-to-queue parser script
   - Writes to: .cache/youtube-dm-inbox.jsonl

2. WEBHOOK INTEGRATION
   - Set up webhook on YouTube Community/Messaging
   - POST JSON to: localhost:8000/youtube-dm
   - Handler appends to: .cache/youtube-dm-inbox.jsonl

3. MANUAL QUEUE
   - Append DM JSON objects to: .cache/youtube-dm-inbox.jsonl
   - Monitor script processes each line

